	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The Dragon Warrior games use this technique extensively for the monster graphics. With the larger monsters in DW3 and DW4, the tile and sprite &quot;layers&quot; noticeably desynchronize when the monsters flash when taking damage.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


